Interface Board

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Caretaker, ObservableModel
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JSynBoard

    public interface Board
extends ObservableModel, Caretaker
    Defines the behavior of a Board, the main Model of our Application.
    Invariant:
    getModules() != null, getModules() != null, getModules().containsValue(getModules()), getCurrentColor() != null

        throws IllegalAccessException,
               InstantiationException
        Creates a new module with the class klass. Return the id of the new Module.
        Parameters:
        klass - the module's class.
        Returns:
        the module identifier.

        InstantiationException - if an instantiation exception occurs.
